column2: back in 1997
column3: Netflix became incorporated. It was founded by Reed Hastings

column2: 1997: Netflix launches as a direct mailing DVD service. 2000: Reed Hastings (Netflix CEO) approaches John Antico (former Blockbuster CEO)
column3: offers to sell for $50 million. Antico declines. August 29
column4: 2018: Netflix has 118 million subscribers and is worth $156 billion. pic.twitter.com/Tvi2Qil2yL"
